  <other_name type="common_name">Cushing’s manzanita</other_name>
  <discussion>Subspecies cushingiana is widespread in mixed populations with subsp. glandulosa
        from Humboldt County in the North Coast Range south to the Peninsular Range, and extending
        into northern Baja California.</discussion>
